<div class="sr-only">
  <h1>About Rose City Robotics</h1>
</div>

<!-- Mission -->
<div id="our-mission" class="mt-32 overflow-hidden sm:mt-40">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:flex lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-12 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:min-w-full lg:max-w-none lg:flex-none lg:gap-y-8">
      <div class="lg:col-end-1 lg:w-full lg:max-w-lg lg:pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600 mt-6">CAD-driven defect detection for precision manufacturers.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700">
          <p>At Rose City Robotics, we build inspection from CAD so quality is defined up front and stays stable on the line. Developed by <a href="/team/joseph-cole-phd/" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-semibold">Joseph Cole, PhD</a>, RoseVision is built for quality and manufacturing engineering teams running high-mix production — shops where visual inspection is impossible to standardize, escaped defects are a real operational risk, and you can't wait months to collect training data before your next revision ships.</p>
          <p class="mt-10">We go beyond thresholds and templates. Upload your STEP file, define the defects that matter, and deploy reliable go/no-go inspection on on-prem edge hardware — no cloud, no fragile rule engines, no full retraining when your CAD changes. Joseph Cole brings 20 years of machine vision and factory automation experience to every engagement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-end gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:contents">
        <div class="w-0 flex-auto lg:ml-auto lg:w-auto lg:flex-none lg:self-end lg:pb-8">
          <img src="<%= relative_url('/images/joe_robot_battery_lab.png') %>" alt="" class="aspect-[7/5] w-full md:w-[37rem] max-w-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Team -->
