    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Team</h2>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">We're machine vision engineers, automation specialists, and manufacturing technologists who've worked in real factories — not just research labs. We partner directly with quality engineers and process engineers who run production: helping design pilots, wiring into robotic cells, and generating the data that makes the business case. We don't hand over software and disappear. Led by Joseph Cole, PhD, we bring 20 years of industrial vision and automation experience to every engagement — and we stay until it works.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <ul role="list" class="mx-auto mt-20 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-20 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-8 xl:max-w-none">
