<!-- Values -->
<div id="our-values" class="mx-auto mt-40 max-w-7xl sm:px-6 sm:mt-40 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Values</h2>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">We believe factory automation should be honest about what it can do, built to last in real production, and delivered by engineers who stand behind their work.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
    <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">Integrity</dt>
        <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">We operate with transparency, not just talk. We're self-capitalized — no VC, no PE, no investor clock ticking. Every decision we make is filtered through one question: does this serve our customers? We don't ask for recurring fees until you have hard data that the system works in your environment.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">Innovation</dt>
        <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">We build from your CAD, not from scratch. From STEP-to-model toolchains to on-prem Jetson deployment, we iterate on real factory constraints — and we show up on the floor to make it work.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">Impact</dt>
        <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">We measure success at the end of the line. Fewer escaped defects. Less over-processing. Unattended runs that actually run unattended. When a quality engineer can walk their VP through a business case built on real pilot data — that's the outcome we're after.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Company -->
<div id="our-company" class="mt-32 overflow-hidden sm:mt-40 mb-40">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:flex lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-12 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:min-w-full lg:max-w-none lg:flex-none lg:gap-y-8">
      <div class="lg:col-end-1 lg:w-full lg:max-w-lg lg:pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Company</h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600 mt-6">Engineering-led. Software-first quality control.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700">
          <p>Rose City Robotics is a Portland-based machine vision lab led by Joseph Cole, PhD. We build inspection from CAD so QA is defined up front and stays stable on the line.</p>
          <p class="mt-6"><strong>RoseVision CAD Studio</strong> turns your design files into deployable inspection logic — ready for on-prem edge hardware like NVIDIA Jetson Orin or x86.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-end gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:contents">
        <div class="w-0 flex-auto lg:ml-auto lg:w-auto lg:flex-none lg:self-end lg:pb-8">
          <div class="relative w-full md:w-[37rem] max-w-none overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gray-100" style="padding-bottom: 56.25%;">
